y dining, fitness studios, beauty services, and the occasional luxury retail activation. The neighborhood's creator community is smaller than Downtown or Brooklyn markets, but highly engaged and well-connected to the spending power that makes campaigns here commercially meaningful."}]]}]}],"$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb"]}]],["$Lc","$Ld"],"$Le"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"jP0DLMf4-wLgFORDq_Yoq"}
